  "notes": [
    {
      "id": "note-investment",
      "title": "Investment Strategy 2024",
      "content": "# Investment Strategy for 2024\n\n## Goals\n- Maximize retirement contributions\n- Diversify portfolio across asset classes\n- Maintain emergency fund\n- Achieve 10% annual returns\n\n## Asset Allocation\n- 60% Stocks (US and International)\n- 25% Bonds\n- 10% Real Estate\n- 5% Cryptocurrency\n\n## Key Principles\n1. **Dollar-cost averaging** for regular investments\n2. **Rebalancing** quarterly\n3. **Tax-loss harvesting** when appropriate\n4. **Long-term focus** - avoid market timing\n\n*Review quarterly and adjust based on market conditions*",
      "notebook": "Financial Planning",
      "tags": [
        "investment",
        "strategy",
        "2024",
        "retirement"
      ],
      "isPinned": true,
      "noteType": "rich",
