    {
      "id": "note-travel",
      "title": "Europe Trip Planning",
      "content": "# Europe Trip Planning - Summer 2024\n\n## Destinations\n1. **Paris, France** (5 days)\n   - Eiffel Tower, Louvre, Notre-Dame\n   - Budget: $1,500\n\n2. **Rome, Italy** (4 days)\n   - Colosseum, Vatican, Trevi Fountain\n   - Budget: $1,200\n\n3. **Barcelona, Spain** (3 days)\n   - Sagrada Familia, Park Güell, Gothic Quarter\n   - Budget: $900\n\n## Total Budget: $4,800\n- Flights: $1,200\n- Hotels: $1,800\n- Food: $800\n- Activities: $600\n- Transportation: $400\n\n## Preparation Checklist\n- [ ] Book flights\n- [ ] Reserve hotels\n- [ ] Get travel insurance\n- [ ] Apply for visas if needed\n- [ ] Plan daily itineraries\n- [ ] Learn basic phrases\n\n*Trip dates: June 15-27, 2024*",
      "notebook": "Travel",
